<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#87a737a7801281e7a790c103eec402b3>.
<#87a737a7801281e7a790c103eec402b3> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/c5050bf711fd4a11b636296b948e921717-42affc57caae79a4>;
