    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessURL> <https://geoservices.wallonie.be/arcgis/services/MOBILITE/VOIESNAVIGABLES/MapServer/WMSServer?request=GetCapabilities&service=WMS>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#accessService> <https://geodata.wallonie.be/id/563eae28-7110-41f6-9201-b1e8f83905d6>;
